[[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Masters]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] could attain the rank of '''Senior Jedi General'''. Ranking immediately below [[High Jedi General/Legends|High Jedi Generals]], Senior Jedi Generals commanded the twenty [[Sector Army/Legends|Sector Armies]] within the [[Grand Army of the Republic/Legends|Grand Army of the Republic]].

Jedi Master [[Luminara Unduli/Legends|Luminara Unduli]] was a Senior Jedi General,<ref name="Vehicles Collection 30">[[Star Wars: The Official Starships & Vehicles Collection 30|''Star Wars: The Official Starships & Vehicles Collection'' 30]]</ref> as was Master [[Ry-Gaul]], who commanded the [[Second Army]].<ref name="GGAR">{{InsiderCite|84|Guide to the Grand Army of the Republic}}</ref>

